				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I would be in favour of a small cooldown...30 secs might be a tiny bit too high, i would like to see 20 secs, but 30 would be bearable. The cooldown would only be per player right? 
<br />

<br />
i.e. Player A sieges player B, and must undergo a 30 sec cooldown, but player C could sige a planet during player A's cooldown?
<br />

<br />
I vaguely remember when their were planet siege cooldowns before, and it was such a pain in the ass because once someone sieged, everyone had a cooldown from sieging the guy...it made it very unfun to war. I would be in support of a cooldown where you could only sige from the guy every 20 or 30 seconds, but not for one where the player goes into a cooldown no one can siege off<br />_________________<br />Houston
<br />

<br />

